[media] usb/gspca/ov519.c: use IS_ENABLED() macro

replace:
 #if defined(CONFIG_INPUT) || \
     defined(CONFIG_INPUT_MODULE)
with:
 #if IS_ENABLED(CONFIG_INPUT)
This change was made for: CONFIG_INPUT

